title: How to Make Shrimp & Mango Dumplings with Sue Chan
description:
Sue Chan, the hostest with the mostest, teaches us how to make shrimp and mango dumplings with an apricot dipping sauce. This recipe has the perfect balance of savory and sweet notes, and—even though it's easy to prepare—will make you look like a true dumpling master.
